315 2088 1783 (libraries run on the Microsoft \(DOS, Windows, Windows 95,
Windows NT\) , IBM \(OS/2\) , and Quantum) 1783 SB
315 2138 1772 (\(QNX\) operating systems.  Some of these platforms involve
multi-threaded capabilities and dynamically-) 1772 SB
