315 2454 1775 (The main discussion will ignore the complications that arise
in multi-threaded environments.  These will) 1775 SB
315 2504 510 (be discussed in a later section.) 510 SB
315 2587 1756 (Global statics are constructed when an image is loaded.  For
a program, this is when the program starts,) 1756 SB
315 2637 1760 (before control has been passed to the mainline.  DLLs can be
created to have a unique data area for each) 1760 SB
315 2687 1757 (program that accesses them, or to have one data area that
